{"tid":1534243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［現在公開可能な情報］9月到底抱咩心態去做人","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:46:09.000Z","uid":301692,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6b75e5f9abf3076793e8a914b8b26171b1089324","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">浩園論李太</div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1️⃣ 拘捕要追quota，似牛肉乾，每日要夠數。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 警察訓練有一項宗旨「痛楚可以令人馴服」<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 地鐵鎚仔廢老係警察安排，制做機會封站<br />\n<br />\n就以上三點請各位手足睇路，和平嘅日子已經結束，要當納粹統治去過生活。因為第二點，請大家有心理準備行出街係會流血係會受傷，示威係會被打，但都請大家一定一定要一齊企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係等於幫左政府戒嚴。因為第三點，手足真係千萬千萬要提高警覺，警察為左執法係會專登犯法，係會無所不用其極地挑撥離間，插贜嫁禍乜都做得出。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭錄音</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">0️⃣ 100%假，擺明星期一流出，內心毫無善意，無辭職被拒呢件事，唔好抱有幻想，屌佢點會無得揀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因有兩個可能性：<br />\n<br />\n(a) 佢自己係屋企錄，篤北京灰，想呃9耶穌俾返天堂個位佢，面對民主法案淆撚晒底，想力挽狂瀾嘿，可惜太遲，<strong>林鄭一定不得善終</strong>。<br />\n(b) 習大大都知道，並默許流出錄音呢件事，令到國內同香港各有各相信版本，保留佢喺國內嘅面子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ 不會明出解放軍，只會靠警察+混公安<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 打消耗戰，拖到唔拖繼續拖。十一都未平息就封鎖消息，國內有國內慶祝。唔太期望美國果邊會再有additional助攻⋯⋯因為站於侵侵立場，佢令到唔出老解已經做左野。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢次係一場長征</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現階段適宜練等，養兵，留力，無乜損耗地捱過民權法案，區議會選舉。到時視情況再打算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蒙臉游擊係目前最有效嘅策略，以武制暴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呢段期間，如果平日決定撚狗一定要打醒十二分精神，<strong>要時刻準備逃命</strong>，因為而家已經係<strong>有理無理都拉</strong>。只係撐場街坊就避免衝突，好配合咁good morning sir，我煲緊湯會火燭呀果種，禮貌啲，弱小市民啲。<strong>轉個頭蒙臉就去燒佢後欄</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左撚狗去練膽，<br />\n仲可以練體能，跑得快啲長氣啲，<br />\n勇武程度要提升，技能未解鎖要解鎖，<br />\n已解鎖魔法嘅玩家，點滿mp，升技升到最短cd<br />\n我地先要變</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">得</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強</span>，<br />\n<strong>先可以喺需要時升級</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家<br />\n已經唔係<br />\n其實由唔知幾時開始，<br />\n己經唔係民意嘅問題。<br />\n係大家各位手足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">夠唔夠血性</span></strong></span>嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只待大家都覺醒，一百萬人一定打得贏三萬人<br />\n<br />\n林鄭嘅軍政府已經無棋，<br />\n得返黑白兩道，打拉告殺四招。<br />\n我地嘅仲有宇宙咁浩瀚嘅潛力未unlock<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2dc7aedf19d789177f779f8596bad747a4ce508d","tid":1534243,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d3ff0c5a33b4a493ffa0d9cd308c2e4f01c5fe8","tid":1534243,"uid":69525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=936dd01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4cfe90645c87887385f6d2402c3b69779df43385","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4ecaa023b4b85c37377dedbf3207f405aed1b2b","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/arZXhRcfEKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FarZXhRcfEKw&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=18f39d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/arZXhRcfEKw</a><br />\n<br />\n補link，又係李太，打上D100嘅片段"},{"pid":"42746a6e972d418b087a6281541800c8fb8fafd6","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"d4666c8fb396ea27637bc24d29631403cdb85b9a","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:19.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"fa3e5a65014895ef8d1e4967088fa5336abe167b","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"0742d41da0b0729e904b3ca05bcbf4fc4f6484b9","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"3cbde24f9a49cea4a83550725b569ec1375e5b51","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"abc23b2d1d31d1ceb46ca41645ee71732ce29292","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"75755574b0515baab2b271703619dae5f695b385","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"f324fbf792b372162bd65468e5fbcfa4b622f076","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"c4b426a600887a298319a125e45386c3f10f4fb6","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"359dc432d7f0957ea7e74bb790ec7c87833ecc07","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:00:37.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"e84fbb29164fda951f87a198ab326ed9a98878fa","tid":1534243,"uid":38494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"ab9039b90c1bb958debe57328b1211d7f907d360","tid":1534243,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaBbTAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaBbTAC.png&h=2beb762c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦一眾考官7號要幫機場重考</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a07049ea6759aaaa5d3d0580cb55841cb13d0c9","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c4261944342b5d5996b6d6c400b07503de459a","tid":1534243,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"好細隻字.....<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=b2382596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=1f18aef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=7c3b432a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png</a>"},{"pid":"c68a201512e8ffab8bc27e78f63777781282b903","tid":1534243,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"還拖呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355076971acbb96a1d7b366eb40a56f2da5b8ae5","tid":1534243,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62c4261944342b5d5996b6d6c400b07503de459a","tid":1534243,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"好細隻字.....<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=b2382596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=1f18aef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.